Subject: [PATCH] 9103: decompiler: Improve decompiler command line

Fix discover ghidra root discovery

Bug occurred when it reached an empty string and didn't exit early
enough.

interface: Add help command

Add help command to print out all available commands.

interface: Support tilde

Expand tilde in `load` commands to $HOME.
